<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Thu, 27 Jul 2023 19:49:36 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Google rolls out anti-stalking measures for AirTag and other Bluetooth trackers]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>谷歌的反跟踪措施正在推出。该公司在 5 月份的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/android-findmy-bluetooth-tracker-google-airtag-tile-182832477.html">Google I/O 大会上宣布</a>的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://blog.google/products/android/unknown-tracker-alert-google-android/">未知跟踪器警报</a>和其他安全措施应该从今天开始出现在 Android 6.0+ 设备上。该举措旨在减少苹果 2021 年推出 AirTag 后不久出现的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airtag-stalking-police-reports-190022315.html">数字跟踪事件</a>。</p><p> Android 的未知跟踪器警报会告诉您是否有未知的蓝牙跟踪器与您同行，但不是其所有者。如果您的 Android 手机通知您发现了跟踪配件，您可以点击警报以了解有关该配件的更多信息，包括该配件与您一起旅行的地点的地图以及（在某些情况下）序列号和有关设备所有者的信息。您还可以点击“播放声音”选项，让配件发出鸣叫声，以帮助您找到它。如果事实证明它是可疑的，它将提供有关停用它的说明，以便其所有者将不再收到更新。 （对于<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airtags-trackers-first-look-hands-on-130036848.html">AirTag</a>来说，这意味着拧开其顶部并取出电池。）</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Android 版本还允许您手动扫描附近的跟踪器，而不是等待警报。您的手机收到更新后，导航至“设置”>;“安全和紧急情况”>;“未知跟踪器警报”，然后选择“立即扫描”按钮。谷歌表示，手动搜索只需要大约十秒钟，如果找到一个，你会看到与收到自动警报相同的选项。</p><p>这项新功能是<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Apple;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4130e2f0-a14f-4c5e-bdab-cd52ac7d8e79&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Apple&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaV_EGo8FZRkAWDMy99T-1zUYUV6g64yuKsWVRDuZjiP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fnewsroom%2F2023%2F05%2Fapple-google-partner-on-an-industry-specification-to-address-unwanted-tracking%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">谷歌和苹果合作</a>解决人们对跟踪器跟踪跟踪问题的成果。此外，谷歌今天宣布，也在 Google I/O 上宣布的“查找我的设备”网络（相当于<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ios-15-find-my-network-tracking-upgrades-032304589.html">苹果的“查找我的</a>”）被推迟。谷歌决定等待苹果在 iOS 中实施其完全未知的跟踪保护，然后再推出新功能。</p><p>请注意，谷歌的反跟踪措施可能会降低在地图上跟踪被盗物品的有效性，因为有进取心的小偷很快就能发现隐藏的跟踪器，无论他们使用哪款手机。然而，可以理解的是，减少跟踪将超越谷歌和苹果安全平衡法案中的担忧。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/google-rolls-out-anti-stalking-measures-for-airtag-and-other-bluetooth-trackers-194936293.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-rolls-out-anti-stalking-measures-for-airtag-and-other-bluetooth-trackers-194936293.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c3333a88-3559-4532-9dc9-cd12108de93b</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jul 2023 19:49:36 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690487378</ingested><modified> 2023-07-27T19:49:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="984" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/9c42dda0-2cb3-11ee-bdde-127adf680105" width="1750"><media:keywords>标题</media